{
  "text": "It is not known whether SP cells isolated from lung truly exhibit bona-fide lung stem cell function [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] but SP-associated drug efflux and resistance to chemotherapies occur in lung and other tissue tumor cell lines in vitro. SP cells have stem cell characteristics including enhanced clonogenicity [CITATION_3] and tumor formation in vivo [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] (Pine and Varticovsky,  unpublished) .",
